name: Open 24 hours Unisex Tee
description:
This awesome tee is a collaboration with Parsons the New School for Design. Ticherts' Creative Director Pati Castellanos had the honor to host a "NYC themed" design workshop. After all the enthusiasm we decided to host a contest within the classroom where professors and the Ticherts' team voted for their favorite. Congrats Kalia Firester, your design won!  

Thank you Parsons for inviting us to share our journey.
*Limited quantity available*

Unisex Tee. Super soft 4.5 oz. 100% combed ring spun cotton jersey knit. Made with Mucho Love.
